</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/851786711055fe57e16e98116fb91d96a112a14b" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.338ex; width:8.006ex; height:2.176ex;" alt="{\displaystyle A\ \to \ \alpha }"></span></dd></dl>
<p>with <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle A}">
