  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/1173552bcbf68bb06baf9b0a2f543dbc845caefd" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:12.259ex; height:2.676ex;" alt="{\displaystyle \alpha A\beta \rightarrow \alpha \gamma \beta }"></span> with <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle A}">
