</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/ed4842d2953d3fcab39e7eb15786b05029b831c5" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:24.972ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="{\displaystyle \langle {\text{Stmt}}\rangle \to \langle {\text{Id}}\rangle =\langle {\text{Expr}}\rangle ;}"></span></dd></dl>
<p>replaces <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle \langle {\text{Stmt}}\rangle }">
