<div class="mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id="Context-free_language">Context-free language</h3><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Context-free_grammar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: Context-free language"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>The language of a grammar <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle G=(V,\Sigma ,R,S)}">
