</p>
<dl><dd><span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle L(G)=\{w\in \Sigma ^{*}:S~{\stackrel {*}{\Rightarrow }}~w\}}">
