<ul><li>unproductive symbols,<sup id="cite&#95;ref-FOOTNOTEHopcroftUllman197988Lemma&#95;4.1&#95;21-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-FOOTNOTEHopcroftUllman197988Lemma_4.1-21"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>19<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup><sup id="cite&#95;ref-23" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-23"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>c<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup></li>
